    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliable performance. The exterior paint still holds a respectable shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it remains solid and drives smoothly, making it an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable, attractive vehicle without the premium price of a mint-condition show car.",
