    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it's never let me down on the road. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend adventure, this ride is ready to hit the pavement. I've taken great care of it, so you're getting a reliable vehicle that's ready to go from day one. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Silver Grey Metallic. Powered by the S54 3.2L straight-six, this high-revving unit features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the powerband. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile engagement, sending power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative work\u2014including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection\u2014is documented, ensuring the chassis handles lateral loads with precision. While the finish exhibits minor patina reflective of its enthusiast use, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a pure analog driving experience with a screaming 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used sedan. Reliable performance. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Recent oil change. Cash only.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
